  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What would be the best attire for me?",
  "response": "Selecting the best attire depends on various factors such as the occasion, your personal style, body type, and the current season or weather conditions. Here are some general guidelines for different types of events:\n\n### Professional or Work Attire:\n1. **Men:** A well-fitted suit in neutral colors like navy, gray, or black, paired with a dress shirt, tie, and polished dress shoes. For business casual, consider dress pants or chinos with a collared shirt and loafers.\n2. **Women:** A tailored dress, skirt, or trousers with a blouse or blazer. Opt for neutral or subtle colors and pair them with closed-toe heels or flats.\n\n### Casual or Everyday Attire:\n1. **Men:** Jeans or chinos paired with t-shirts, polo shirts, or casual button-down shirts. Sneakers, loafers, or casual boots can complete the look.\n2. **Women:** Comfortable jeans, leggings, or casual dresses paired with t-shirts, blouses, or sweaters. Casual shoes like sneakers, flats, or ankle boots are ideal.\n\n### Formal or Evening Attire:\n1. **Men:** A tuxedo or formal suit with a dress shirt, bow tie, and polished dress shoes. Ensure the fit is impeccable and consider cufflinks for an added touch.\n2. **Women:** A cocktail dress, evening gown, or elegant pantsuit. Pair with high heels and sophisticated accessories like jewelry and a clutch.\n\n### Seasonal Attire:\n1. **Spring/Summer:** Light, breathable fabrics such as cotton or linen. Opt for lighter colors and patterns. Men can wear shorts, short-sleeve shirts, or lightweight suits. Women can choose sundresses, skirts, or lightweight trousers and tops.\n2. **Fall/Winter:** Warmer, layered clothing such as sweaters, coats, scarves, and boots. Men can wear wool suits, flannel shirts, and heavier trousers. Women can opt for layered skirts, dresses with tights, or cozy sweaters and coats.\n\n### Athletic or Leisure Attire:\n1. **Men:** Athletic shorts, joggers, or sweatpants paired with moisture-wicking shirts or hoodies. Comfortable athletic shoes are essential.\n2. **Women:** Leggings, yoga pants, or athletic shorts paired with tank tops, sports bras, or moisture-wicking shirts. Comfortable athletic shoes are ideal.\n\n### Personal Style:\nConsider your unique preferences and comfort. Whether you prefer classic, trendy, bohemian, preppy, or minimalist styles, choose outfits that make you feel confident and express your personality.\n\n### Body Type:\nSelect clothing that flatters your body type. For example, tailored pieces can enhance your shape, while looser styles can provide a relaxed fit. \n\nUltimately, the best attire is one that suits the occasion, your personal taste, and makes you feel comfortable and confident.",
